</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-fKWLGC lflwGM pf-499_">Share data, funding, and innovation in ways that strengthen global health equity.
</li></ul></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="sc-hzhKNl fltMam pf-109_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-bkSTSn hpQOMO pf-110_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-kRRxPL kSaugo pf-111_">The opportunity ahead - From applause to action
